       fhir:ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description [ fhir:value "Documents the patient's pre-existing medical/surgical history (eHistory.08) as reported during an EMS response. Condition.code carries the ICD-10-CM history code; advance directives, history source, immunizations, alcohol/drug indicators, pregnancy, and last oral intake are captured in the ext-ems-history-context extension. Create one resource per reported condition." ] ;
