       fhir:ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.name [ fhir:value "EMS Outcome Observation" ] ;
       fhir:ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description [ fhir:value "Documents hospital and ED outcome data collected by the EMS agency. Covers NEMSIS eOutcome.01 (ED Disposition), eOutcome.02 (Hospital Disposition), eOutcome.09/12 (ED/Hospital Procedures using ICD-10-PCS), eOutcome.10/13 (ED/Hospital Diagnoses using ICD-10-CM), eOutcome.11 (Hospital Admission DateTime), eOutcome.16 (Hospital Discharge DateTime), eOutcome.18 (ED Admission DateTime), and eOutcome.21 (Injury Severity Score). Each significant eOutcome data point is captured as an Observation component." ] ;
